{"word":"G2818 - κληρονόμος - klēronómos - klay-ron-om'-os - Heir","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κληρονόμος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>klēronómos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>klay-ron-om'-os"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Heir"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"சுதந்தரவாளி, சுதந்திரர் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"an heir"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G2819 - κλῆρος - klēros - klay'-ros/2819\">G2819</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G3551 - νόμος - nómos - nom'-os/3551\">G3551</a> (in its original sense of <i>partitioning</i>, that is, [reflexively] <i>getting</i> by apportionment); a <i>sharer by lot</i>, that is, an <i>inheritor</i> (literally or figuratively); by implication a <i>possessor:</i> - heir."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2624 - κατακληροδοτέω - kataklērodotéō - kat-ak-lay-rod-ot-eh'-o/2624\">G2624</a>, <a href=\"#/G2816 - κληρονομέω - klēronoméō - klay-ron-om-eh'-o/2816\">G2816</a>, <a href=\"#/G2817 - κληρονομία - klēronomía - klay-ron-om-ee'-ah/2817\">G2817</a>, <a href=\"#/G2818 - κληρονόμος - klēronómos - klay-ron-om'-os/2818\">G2818</a>, <a href=\"#/G2819 - κλῆρος - klēros - klay'-ros/2819\">G2819</a>, <a href=\"#/G2820 - κληρόω - klēróō - klay-ro'-o/2820\">G2820</a>, <a href=\"#/G3647 - ὁλοκληρία - holoklēría - hol-ok-lay-ree'-ah/3647\">G3647</a>, <a href=\"#/G3648 - ὁλόκληρος - holóklēros - hol'-ok'-lay-ros/3648\">G3648</a>, <a hre